---------------------------------------------------Project Wroking Structure--------------------------------------------------

React Frontend
      ↓
Axios for API Calls
      ↓
Django REST API
      ↓
Business Logic (Views)
      ↓
MySQL Database
      ↓
Response (JSON)
      ↓
React UI Display